# QA Automation Framework #

The QA Automation Framework was designed to cover E2E UI tests using BDD with Cucumber and Selenium base on Java.

## Prerequisites
* Java JDK 17
* Maven
* IntelliJ
* JUnit
* Cucumber
* Selenium
* Selenium WebDriver


## How to run the framework? ###
You can run tests by a Maven command.
The command could be used by the command line or in your favorite IDE.

mvn clean verify -Dcucumber.filter.tags="[tags]"

Example: clean verify -Dcucumber.filter.tags=@LogInPageNavigation

## Reporting
### Cucumber report
It's available for local (under target folder) or GitHub workflow running


